{"tid":1359631,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"美國媒體對TWICE的演唱會評論 ONCE們很生氣","createTime":"2019-07-24T07:30:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T05:35:04.000Z","uid":74065,"like":32,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"6676590f20f02c7f2b2b9826e1bf1e4731e09224","tid":1359631,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:30:20.000Z","msg":"一個美國當地新聞媒體最近上傳了許多關於TWICE在美國最新演唱會的負面評論<br />\n<br />\nTWICE的世界巡迴演唱會&ldquo; TWICELIGHTS &rdquo; 的最新舉辦地點是紐瓦克（美國）。<br />\n像往常一樣，TWICE為粉絲帶來了最好的表演。<br />\n然而，當地新聞來源並不讚賞他們的努力。<br />\n<a href=\"http://NJ.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FNJ.com&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTe%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=332182bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">NJ.com</a>上的一篇文章標題為&ldquo; K-pop轟動TWICE在新澤西州第一場演唱會上是一個非常蓬鬆的失敗：評論 &rdquo;在本文作者嚴厲批評JYP娛樂公司的9名女孩之後立即成為關注和辯論的中心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://kbizoom.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/twicenjcom1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkbizoom.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2Ftwicenjcom1.png&h=81d05246&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在整篇文章中，作者不斷提到TWICE的成功不值得，而且他們在美國的受歡迎程度&ldquo;超大&rdquo;。TWICE也被認為是沒有天賦的，&ldquo; 充滿熱情，或任何超過人才，可以在YouTube上獲得25億次觀看 &rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n這個人繼續說，只有3名成員可以在沒有後道幫助的情況下保持曲調：&ldquo; 隨著震耳欲聾的集合開始，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">很明顯只有兩三個女性 - 該組織中最外向的成員，Nayeon; <br />\n該集團的官方&ldquo;領導者&rdquo;和完美的領導者，Jihyo; <br />\nJeongyeon - 在沒有PA的背景音軌的支持下，實際上可以保持一個曲調。<br />\n該組的其餘成員只是被動地同步，很少獨奏。&ldquo;</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://kbizoom.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/twicejaoan12more3-1024x576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkbizoom.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2Ftwicejaoan12more3-1024x576.jpg&h=12c269a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然而，缺乏表演能力是最令人不快的。<br />\n<br />\n只有Nayeon看起來她真的想要在那裡。而且，儘管看了兩個多小時，我還是不知道這些女人是誰。<br />\n<br />\n也許這是一種文化差異，女性自然而然地更加保守，或者被指示在任何時刻都散發出一種熠熠生輝的選美姿態。無論如何，這個群體都感覺到了電子動畫。<br />\n<br />\n這個行為被JYP的權力命名為TWICE，因為樂隊應該通過音樂和視覺來吸引粉絲。<br />\n<br />\nBoth need work.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">K-pop sensation TWICE was a <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>big fluffy flop</strong></span> at 1st N.J. concert: review</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nj.com/entertainment/2019/07/k-pop-sensation-twice-was-a-big-fluffy-flop-at-1st-nj-concert-review.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nj.com%2Fentertainment%2F2019%2F07%2Fk-pop-sensation-twice-was-a-big-fluffy-flop-at-1st-nj-concert-review.html&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTe%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=2b972126\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nj.com/entertainment/2019/07/k-pop-sensation-twice-was-a-big-fluffy-flop-at-1st-nj-concert-review.html</a><br />\n<br />\n利申 太長用GOOGLE TRANSLATE 原文自己睇"},{"pid":"e3d1859dafdf526f5ec7469363073633737ddcbb","tid":1359631,"uid":138138,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:33:24.000Z","msg":"因為樂隊應該通過音樂和視覺來吸引粉絲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有咩？？"},{"pid":"b2db27709105b57b3fea8c7fde5f4efdb31cf0db","tid":1359631,"uid":3405,"like":42,"dislike":3,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:34:10.000Z","msg":"講事實又嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f2c869e1d9501b00325fa868df364aafcbd59e","tid":1359631,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:38:45.000Z","msg":"我也生氣了"},{"pid":"e8bb3c12af3562856ee9610d96cc6e41e42b5254","tid":1359631,"uid":555,"like":31,"dislike":4,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:50:44.000Z","msg":"同一篇野開2個post<br />\nAdmin請ban樓主惡意灌水"},{"pid":"00a537e6bb27fac7fbdece6d742aaa21e3b2c419","tid":1359631,"uid":138658,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:04:05.000Z","msg":"正常人點會對兒歌有期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff8cffe94fe7696150b3e82efe08999728146db","tid":1359631,"uid":208486,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-